    "source_text": "Note that \\alpha ^ { ( 1 ) } given therein corresponds to \\beta and \\beta ^ { ( 1 ) } to \\alpha (according to Eqs. 4 and 5). Thus for \\omega B97X, the parameter used to calculate \\gamma _ { A B } ^ { J } is \\beta = 8 . 0 0 .",
